$columnMappings

$columnMappings : array

Type

array — Define the rules how the file transform into the wanted model The rule can be simple as the field name, or a configuration array. possible configuration option, please @see DataMapping this configuration array is mapped to data columns one by one. if the field index is different from the element index in this array, please specific colIndex attribute One example: ```php [ 'field1', [ 'field' => 'field2' 'required' => true, 'colIndex' => 4, 'translation' => function($orgValue) { return $newValue; } ], ... ] ```
